headline: dbt Labs Signs Strategic Collaboration Agreement with AWS
summary: dbt Labs, the leader in standards for AI-ready structured data, today announced it has signed a strategic collaboration agreement (SCA) with Amazon Web Services (AWS). The agreement will expand technical integrations across services including Amazon Redshift, Amazon Athena, and Amazon SageMaker Lakehouse, while also expanding AWS Marketplace availability to simplify access and procurement for enterprise customers.
